		<arrangement encodinganalog="MARC 351$a">
			<head id="a4">COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT</head>
			<p>The records are arranged in three series: I. Photographs; II. Correspondence; III.
				Computer files.</p>
			<p>The arrangement is roughly chronological.</p>
